data.description: Welcome to Taylor Ridge in Hampton, GA - a place where elegance meets modern comfort. Nestled within this exquisite subdivision lies a beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home that exudes charm and sophistication. This meticulously maintained residence boasts upgraded granite countertops, enhancing the allure of its well-appointed kitchen. The inclusion of storm doors and a water filtration system reflects the thoughtful consideration for both practicality and luxury. As an added assurance, this resplendent abode comes complete with a comprehensive home warranty, underscoring the commitment to providing peace of mind to its future residents. Furthermore, the privacy fence surrounding the backyard offers a serene retreat, perfect for unwinding in quiet seclusion or hosting intimate gatherings. With every meticulous detail thoughtfully attended to, this home embodies the epitome of refined living. It is a testament to the harmonious balance between elegance, functionality, and comfort. Welcome home to a place where sophistication and serenity converge seamlessly.
